13 amended and reenacted as follows:
14 23.1-07-05. Fees.
15 The department may charge a fee for certificates issued under this chapter, but the fees
16 may not exceed fifty dollars for the initial certificate, or twenty-five dollars for the annual renewal
17 certificateby rule may prescribe and provide for the payment and collection of reasonable fees
