6 SECTION 5. A new section to chapter 23.1-07 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
7 and enacted as follows:
8 Administrative procedure and judicial review.
9 1. A proceeding under this chapter to adopt or modify rules relating to the certification
10 and regulation of water distribution and wastewater system operators, or for
11 determining compliance with rules of the department, must be conducted in
12 accordance with the provisions of chapter 28 - 32 .
